import React from 'react';
import { Typography, Grid, Link } from '@material-ui/core';
import MailIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Mail';
import LinkedInIcon from '@material-ui/icons/LinkedIn';

const Footer = () => {
    return (
        <Grid container
        direction="row"
        justify="flex-start"
        alignItems="center"
        style={{height:'100px', backgroundColor:'rgba(0,0,0,0.7)'}}>
            <Grid item sm={4}>
            </Grid>

            <Grid item sm={4}>

                <Grid container
                direction="column"
                justify="center"
                alignItems="left">

                    <Grid item xs={12}>

                        <Grid container
                        direction="row"
                        justify="center"
                        alignItems="right">
                            <Grid item xs={2}><MailIcon style={{color:'white'}}/></Grid>
                            <Grid item xs={10}>
                                <Typography
                                style={{color:'white'}}>
                                andrea.husseiniova@gmail.com
                                </Typography>
                            </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                    </Grid>

                    <Grid item xs={12}>
                        <Grid container
                            direction="row"
                            justify="center"
                            alignItems="center">
                                <Grid item xs={2}><LinkedInIcon style={{color:'white'}}/></Grid>
                                <Grid item xs={10}>
                                    <Typography
                                    style={{color:'white'}}>
                                    Andrea Husseiniova
                                    </Typography>
                                </Grid>
                        </Grid>
                    </Grid>

                    </Grid>
                </Grid>

            <Grid item sm={4}>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>

    )
}

export default Footer;
